snippet.title: The Red Lantern - Releases October 22nd, 2020!
snippet.description:
The Red Lantern arrives on PC via the Epic Games Store and on Nintendo Switch on October 22nd, 2020. Wishlist it today, and buy it during our launch sale to save 20%!

The Red Lantern is a story-driven, rogue-lite game where you and your team of 5 sled dogs must navigate the ever-changing Alaskan wilderness to find your way home. Adopt the dogs to fill out your team, discover the items that will help you survive, tend to your team, and make sure they're well fed and pet.
